Features

🛍️ Product listing and details page

👤 User authentication & admin access

🛒 Shopping cart functionality

💳 Order processing system

🌐 Responsive and fast frontend (Next.js + Tailwind CSS)

📡 REST API powered backend (Express + MongoDB)

Technologies Used

Frontend: Next.js, React, Tailwind CSS

Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose

Other: dotenv, cors